==English==

{{rank|anything|matter|passed|291|true|friend|herself|year}}

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /truː/
===Adjective===
'''true'''
#(of a statement) [[concur]]ring with a given set of [[fact]]s.
#(''logic'') A state in Boolean [[logic]] that indicates an [[affirmative]] or positive result.
#:A and B'' is true if and only if ''A'' is true and ''B'' is true.''
#Loyal, faithful.
#:''He's turned out to be a true friend.''
#Genuine.
#:''This is a true Parmesan cheese.''
#Legitimate.
#:''The true king has returned!''
====Antonyms====
*[[false]] (1,2,3)

